ghostctl (1.0.1-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * New upstream release v1.0.1
  * Gaming Module Completion
    - Fully implemented all missing gaming components
    - Added comprehensive gaming optimization features
    - Integrated into main GhostCTL menu system
  * Arch Module Major Enhancement
    - Dramatically expanded performance tuning system
    - Added advanced system administration module
    - Enterprise-level features
  * Code Quality & Compilation
    - Fixed all compilation errors
    - Resolved borrow checker issues
    - Built successfully with minimal warnings
  * Native scanner implemented - replaced gscan with native Rust
  * Enterprise features integrated
  * All modules accessible through menu system
  * No system-breaking changes

